pycairo: pycairo (Cairo Bindings for Cairo)
pycairo:
pycairo: Cairo is a 2D graphics library with support for multiple output
pycairo: devices. Currently supported output targets include the X Window 
pycairo: System, Win32, image buffers, PostScript, PDF, and SVG file output. 
pycairo: Cairo is designed to produce consistent output on all output media 
pycairo: while taking advantage of display hardware acceleration when
pycairo: available (eg. through the X Render Extension).
pycairo:
pycairo: Pycairo is set of Python bindings for the Cairo graphics library.
pycairo:
